## API: getAllFriends

### Description
Retrieve the friend list of the currently logged-in Zalo account.

This API returns a list of all friends associated with the authenticated account.  
Supports pagination via `count` and `page`.

---

### Method (zca-js)
api.getAllFriends()

---

### Parameters

- count: number (optional)  
  → Number of friends per page (default: 20000)

- page: number (optional)  
  → Page number (default: 1)

---

### Example

```ts
const friends = await api.getAllFriends();
console.log(friends);
```

---

### Return

```ts
User[]
```

- Array of User objects  
  → Each item represents a Zalo friend

