## API: findUser

### Description
Find a Zalo user by phone number.

This API retrieves user profile information based on a phone number.  
It is commonly used to convert a phone number into a `userId` (uid) for further operations.

---

### Method (zca-js)
api.findUser(phoneNumber)

---

### Parameters

- phoneNumber: string  
  → Phone number of the user

---

### Example

```ts
const user = await api.findUser("0909090909");
console.log(user);
```

---

### Return

```ts
{
  avatar: string;
  cover: string;
  status: string;
  gender: Gender;
  dob: number;
  sdob: string;
  globalId: string;
  bizPkg: ZBusinessPackage;
  uid: string;
  zalo_name: string;
  display_name: string;
}
```

- uid  
  → Zalo user ID (MOST IMPORTANT)

- display_name / zalo_name  
  → User name

- avatar  
  → Profile image

- Other fields  
  → Additional metadata

---